OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FIan Brown from the Stone Roses
OL,7,Ffamously said "Manchester has
OL,8,Feverything except a beach". Turns out
OL,9,Fit just hadn't been built yet.
OL,11,FThe Therme Wellness Resort in the
OL,12,Fheart of Bucharest is the blue print
OL,13,Ffor Manchester.
OL,15,FManchester may be famous for its
OL,16,Fmusic, football and, of course, its
OL,17,Frain... so why a beach?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
