OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779217874
OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FA vast new wellness resort planned for
OL,7,FTrafford is aiming to bring something
OL,8,Fnew to the area, to improve people's
OL,9,Fhealth.
OL,11,FInspired by the sprawling Therme
OL,12,Fcomplex in Bucharest, developers say
OL,13,Fthe half a billion pound project will
OL,14,Fcreate the world's largest wellbeing
OL,15,Fspa right in the heart of Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
