PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779217874
OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FSet across 30 acres ` the equivalent
OL,7,Fof 18 football pitches ` Therme
OL,8,FManchester is scheduled to open in
OL,9,F2028. Its design is based on
OL,10,Freconnecting people with water and
OL,11,Fnature, blending thermal bathing
OL,12,Ftraditions that date back to Ancient
OL,13,FRome with modern leisure and wellness
OL,14,Fexperiences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
