FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779217874
OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FFor those unfamiliar with the concept,
OL,7,FDeana Boamfa, Marketing and Events
OL,8,FManager at Therme Bucharest, describes
OL,9,Fit simply: "It's going to be love at
OL,10,Ffirst sight. Everything is in one
OL,11,Fplace. Whether people want adrenaline,
OL,12,Frelaxation, or time to reconnect with
OL,13,Fthemselves ` you have everything."
OL,26,@qD@LOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
