FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779217874
OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FThe Manchester site will be divided
OL,7,Finto zones focused on "play", "rest"
OL,8,Fand "restore". Visitors can expect
OL,9,Fwater slides and family attractions,
OL,10,Falongside thermal pools heated to 33
OL,11,Fdegrees, relaxation areas, and
OL,12,Ftreatments designed to boost both
OL,13,Fphysical and mental wellbeing.
OL,15,FWork began on the Trafford site last
OL,16,FSeptember, and anticipation is already
OL,17,Fbuilding ` not least among the team
OL,18,Fbehind the original resort. "I'm
OL,19,Fsuper, super excited," Boamfa said.
OL,20,F"This place is going to have another
OL,21,Fsister."
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@\O]oD@_OUoD@dO]pD@EOUpD@MO]zD@
OL,26,A]OU{D@VO]|D@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
