OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FBut with the UK still facing a cost of
OL,7,Fliving squeeze, questions remain about
OL,8,Fwhether a luxury wellness destination
OL,9,Fwill be within reach for most people.
OL,11,FJonathan Lingman, Commercial Director
OL,12,Ffor Therme Manchester, insists
OL,13,Faffordability is central to the
OL,14,Fproject.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's very important to us to
OL,17,Fmake sure that it is accessible to
OL,18,Fall," he said. "We want young
OL,19,Ffamilies, pensioners ` everyone in
OL,20,Fbetween. Pricing has to work for
OL,21,Feveryone, and it will."
OL,26,@xD@JOUzD@EO]zD@POU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
