OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FDevelopers are also hoping to tap into
OL,7,Fchanging social habits, particularly
OL,8,Famong younger generations who are
OL,9,Fmoving away from traditional nightlife
OL,10,Ftowards health-focused activities.
OL,12,F"There's been a real shift in
OL,13,Fattitudes," Lingman added. "People are
OL,14,Fthinking more about both physical and
OL,15,Fmental wellbeing. The idea of spending
OL,16,Ftime together ` swimming, relaxing,
OL,17,Fbreathing in fresh air ` it makes
OL,18,Fpeople feel better."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@KO]uD@\OUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
