OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FAt the Bucharest site, that philosophy
OL,7,Fincludes treatments designed to make
OL,8,Fwellness engaging ` even intense. One
OL,9,Fof the most talked-about is "Venom
OL,10,FStrike", where therapists massage bee
OL,11,Fvenom into the body before using high-
OL,12,Ffrequency vibration techniques.
OL,14,F"Wellness should be available every
OL,15,Fsingle day," said Cosmin Ciric,
OL,16,FDirector of Wellness at Therme
OL,17,FBucharest. "We make health fun.
OL,18,FPrevention and longevity should be
OL,19,Fpart of everyday life."
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@GO]vD@AOUwD@LO]yD@LOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
