FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779217874
OL,3,CWorld's largest spa coming to
OL,4,CManchester - but will it be affordable?
OL,6,FBack in Manchester, the scale of the
OL,7,Fproject is as ambitious as its vision.
OL,8,FThe resort aims to attract around two
OL,9,Fmillion visitors a year, supporting
OL,10,Fits goal of keeping prices accessible.
OL,12,FIt is also expected to create nearly
OL,13,F2,000 construction jobs and around 800
OL,14,Fpermanent roles once open.
OL,16,FFor a city better known for drizzle
OL,17,Fthan thermal waters, the development
OL,18,Fcould mark a significant shift `
OL,19,Fbringing a new tourist attraction to
OL,20,Fthe North West.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
